  { problem: "We do not know what is working", solution: "No conversion tracking means flying blind. We set up complete GA4 and Google Ads tracking so you know exactly which keyword sent which lead and what it cost." },
  { problem: "Our previous agency kept increasing our budget but not our results", solution: "More budget without better targeting just burns more money. We optimise first, then scale only what is proven to work." },
  { problem: "Our ads show but no one clicks", solution: "Low click-through rate means weak ad copy or wrong audience. We write ads that match search intent and test multiple versions every month to find what converts." },
  { problem: "We tried Google Ads ourselves and it did not work", solution: "Self-managed campaigns almost always lose money. Google's automated suggestions are designed to spend your budget, not save it. Expert management typically reduces wasted spend by 40 to 60 percent." },
];

